{"tid":263603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分析指WannaCry幕後犯罪分子「以中文為母語」　勒索信息文法較準確","createTime":"2017-05-30T07:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T14:04:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0605ce7e8b1cea39b3ef72644cfe86c0d0344d5","tid":263603,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"根據美國情報公司「Flashpoint」的語言分析，這病毒軟件發布的勒索信息多達28種語言，但只有中文版本在語法和標點符號使用上「非常地道」，顯示寫中文版勒索信息的人是以中文為母語或中文極其流利。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員指，中文版的勒索信文法準確，篇幅較長，而且很有可能是用拼音輸入，因為「幫助」（bang zhu）寫成了「幫組」（bang zu），另外，「week」用「禮拜」來表達，符合中國南方、香港、台灣及新加坡華人的使用習慣，還有「anti-virus」用的是「殺毒軟件」來表示，符合中國人的說法。<br />\n<br />\n分析相信只有中文版及英文版的勒索信息是真人寫成，其他語言則似乎是由Google翻譯，但英文版亦有使用了一些不常用的詞句，如「但你沒有足夠時間」時則寫成「But you have not so enough time」。<br />\n<br />\n早前調查人員曾懷疑WannaCry背後的犯罪分子正匿藏朝鮮，但Flashpoint指出，勒索信息中的朝鮮版是從英文版翻譯過去，而且翻譯水平很差。<br />\n<br />\n（英國廣播公司/CNET）<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170530/s00005/1496103043138#sthash.dhs0FSdp.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170530%2Fs00005%2F1496103043138%23sthash.dhs0FSdp.dpuf&d=vrhZnDHKW51tj3WzTCWD%2BTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a3d4b270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170530%2Fs00005%2F1496103043138%23sthash.dhs0FSdp.dpuf&h=069fb8ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170530/s00005/1496103043138#sthash.dhs0FSdp.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"2773d9a0676882f1249e8586724152bd36c0b93d","tid":263603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"學外語既重要性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45a1559d3d09dc5f70fb1e51eb6c0aeafcd032c","tid":263603,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"寫程式同寫